IEC 60027為[[国际电工委员会|国际电工委员会]]的电气技术用字母符号標準。分為以下幾個部份：
* IEC 60027-1: General 总则
* IEC 60027-2: Telecommunications and electronics 电信和电子学
* IEC 60027-3: Logarithmic and related quantities, and their units 对数量和单位
* IEC 60027-4: Symbols for quantities to be used for rotating electrical machines 旋转电机用量值符号
* IEC 60027-6: Control technology 控制技术
* IEC 60027-7: Physiological quantities and units

==二進制前綴==
{{main|二進制前綴}}
1999年新增的IEC 60027-2<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/binary.html |title=NIST summary of IEC 60027-2 |accessdate=2010-06-21 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527081253/https://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/binary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>定義了kilobit不可代表kibibit。

統一的[[ISO|ISO]]/[[国际电工委员会|IEC]] [[ISO/IEC_80000|IEC 80000-13:2008]]標準取消並取代第3.8和3.9的IEC 60027-2:2005（二進制前綴倍數），唯一的改變是增加了明確的定義和一些數量。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.niso.org/publications/newsline/2008/newslinemay2008.htm#Spec4 |title=niso, New Specs and Standards |accessdate=2010-06-21 |archive-date=2008-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208131408/http://www.niso.org/publications/newsline/2008/newslinemay2008.htm#Spec4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

